	<Fixlet>
		<Title>Updated ESX Client - IBM BigFix version 9.2.17 Now Available!</Title>
		<Description><![CDATA[
<DIV class=FixletMessage>
<TABLE><TBODY><TR><TD><P><FONT size=2><FONT color=#ff0000><FONT color=#000000><STRONG>Version 9.2.17 of IBM BigFix is now available!<BR><BR></STRONG>The latest version of the IBM BigFix Client provides several enhancements and fixes. This Fixlet message will upgrade Clients on all targeted computers. <BR><BR></FONT><STRONG><FONT color=red>You must upgrade your Relays to a 9.2 version before upgrading your Clients.</FONT><BR><BR><FONT color=#000000>Note: </FONT></STRONG></FONT><FONT color=#000000>This Fixlet message will only become relevant on computers after the IBM BigFix Server has been upgraded. It may take several hours for the Clients to notice that the IBM BigFix Server is upgraded.<BR><BR><STRONG>Note: </STRONG>It is recommended that you run this upgrade targeted to "All Computers" rather than to "Specific Computers" so that all old Clients will get upgraded.<BR><BR><STRONG>Note: </STRONG>This upgrade may take several minutes to run because the Client service will be restarted as part of the upgrade process and the Clients will not report their action results right away.</FONT></FONT></P></TD></TR></TBODY></TABLE>
</DIV>
<DIV class=FixletProperty>
<H4>File Size:</H4>
15.7 MB
 </DIV>
]]></Description>
